snippet.title: Super Mario Moonlight - F3 2024 Trailer
snippet.description:
Super Mario Moonlight is a mod for Super Mario 3D World + Bowser's Fury that adds an entirely new world full of levels that will be released in the summer of this year! This is the final trailer before the full release.

Lead Developer/Trailer: Floaty (https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCpmyWA7vS2jkgKg753LPmrQ)
Camaras/Extra Help: Parax342 (https://www.youtube.com/@Parax342)
Extra Model Help: AlexSMG (https://www.youtube.com/@alexsmg5298)
Trailer Music: NoteBlock (https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3zdZNnjVrfg) 

Moonlight Discord Server: https://discord.com/invite/AP934GUch6
3DW Modding Discord Server: https://discord.gg/5uskscDR3m
Twitter: https://twitter.com/Floaty01
